attr.title: Ne Touchez Pas 5
attr.desc: Navigate 100 levels with six unique characters, each with distinct controls. Dodge deadly fans, evade lasers, hit switches, collect bits, and leap into the void to progress.
attr.inst: Purchase the full game at itch.io (https://ci.itch.io/ne-touchez-pas-5). Download and extract the .zip, and copy the game files to this port's gamedata folder.
attr.inst_md: Purchase the full game at [itch.io](https://ci.itch.io/ne-touchez-pas-5). Download and extract the *.zip*, and copy the game files to this port's *gamedata* folder.
